snippet.title: REKOR BARU GAME TERCEPAT | RRQ HOSHI MPL S15 HIGHLIGHT
snippet.description:
RRQ Hoshi harus menghadapi Sang Juara MPL ID S14 yaitu Team Liquid ID di minggu kedua Mobile Legends Professional League (MPL) ID Season 15. Pertarungan yang digadang-gadang akan sengit, nyatanya berbeda, karena RRQ Hoshi berhasil memenangkan game pertama dengan one-sided game, dan game kedua berhasil memecahkan rekor baru di MPL ID dengan game tercepat yaitu 9 menit 40 detik.

Semoga mereka bisa terus mempertahankan performa yang baik ini hingga akhir musim ya, Kingdom!

Yuk gabung menjadi member channel ini:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCsE7IVpsU-jk6vAdBP9ZREg/join

All about Team RRQ :
Website : https://teamrrq.com/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Team.RRQ/
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/teamrrq/
Official Merchandise : https://store.teamrrq.com

Diranah minang nagari kito
Sabimbiangan tangan dihari kamanangan

Dimana pun berada bulan

Dek hari kamanangan nan alah tibo

Mari sama sama kita jaga toleransi
Dari hati di bulan suci
Hormati yang puasa kita ju puasa
Takjil sama sama kita satu indonesia

Mari torang salam salaman
Mari torang maaf maafan
Fitri tanda kemenangan

Adu ee buang semua sifat buruk itu le
Jang sampe orang pikir te bae
Adu adu e jang suka tagae deng putar bale
Senyum sambut hari kemenangan le

snippet.title: HIGHLIGHTS | Arsenal vs Chelsea (1-0) | Premier League | Merino with the winner!
snippet.description:
Mikel Merino’s first-half header was enough to win a hotly-contested London derby against Chelsea.

The Spaniard – starting his sixth consecutive game up front – flicked in Martin Odegaard’s corner to give us a deserved lead on 20 minutes.

There were few clear-cut chances for either side after that, though Merino came closest to doubling our advantage in the second-half, with a well-struck volley that Robert Sanchez batted away.

But the one goal was enough to consolidate our second-position in the table, while also making it seven successive Premier League games against Chelsea without defeat.

We racked up six attempts in an opening 20 minutes full of attacking intent.

Within the first five minutes Jurrien Timber headed a corner wide of the near post before Leandro Trossard skewed a shot wide when he had a bit of time to set his shot on the edge of the box.

Gabriel Martinelli – back in the starting lineup for the first time for over a month – was presented with our next chance from a wayward Sanchez pass. His shot was straight at the Spaniard though.

Chelsea survived a penalty shout for handball against Marc Cucurella, who appeared to divert the ball away from Timber with his arm as he fell. We carried on, and after a scramble in the six-yard box, Declan Rice blasted his shot over.

Rice then struck wide from 25 yards as we continued to put the visitors under pressure. Trossard was next to try his luck. Sanchez failed to collect a cross, but our Belgian forward scuffed his right-footed attempt off target.

The goal was coming, and eventually our pressure paid off. Martinelli ran at Benoit Badiashile on the right to win a corner, which Odegaard swung in from the left. Merino ran across the front post, and flicked his header over Sanchez.

Chelsea were fortunate to still have 11 men on the pitch when Wesley Fofana survived a VAR review after an apparent stamp on Rice.

It had been one-way traffic from the opening half hour, but Chelsea nearly drew level when Cucurella’s speculative shot squirmed through David Raya’s grasp but luckily just the wrong side of the upright.

It was a warning from the visitors who were slowly starting to build up possession. We finished the first-half back on top though, and Trossard so nearly set up Odegaard inside the area, but his pass was intercepted.

It was a slower start to the second half, but we woke up when Martinelli’s deep cross fell beautifully onto the left boot of Merino. He cracked his volley goalwards but Sanchez parried the effort on his goalline.

Odegaard was the next to draw a save from Sanchez, but his first-time left footed effort inside the area lacked power.

Rice saw his free-kick deflected wide after Myles Lewis-Skelly earned the set piece with a positive driving run.

There was less goalmouth action in the second-half, but the intensity remained, and both sides had three players in the book by the 70th minute.

Mikel Arteta sent on Ethan Nwaneri late on, but we couldn’t add to the scoreline, making for a fairly edgy last 15 minutes, though in truth Raya remained untroubled in goal.

#arsenal

It was a warning from the visitors who were slowly starting to build up possession. We finished the first-half back on top though, and Trossard so nearly set up Odegaard inside the area, but his pass was intercepted.

It was a slower start to the second half, but we woke up when Martinelli’s deep cross fell beautifully onto the left boot of Merino. He cracked his volley goalwards but Sanchez parried the effort on his goalline.

Odegaard was the next to draw a save from Sanchez, but his first-time left footed effort inside the area lacked power.

Rice saw his free-kick deflected wide after Myles Lewis-Skelly earned the set piece with a positive driving run.

There was less goalmouth action in the second-half, but the intensity remained, and both sides had three players in the book by the 70th minute.

Mikel Arteta sent on Ethan Nwaneri late on, but we couldn’t add to the scoreline, making for a fairly edgy last 15 minutes, though in truth Raya remained untroubled in goal.

en-GB.title: HIGHLIGHTS | Arsenal vs Chelsea (1-0) | Premier League | Merino with the winner!
en-GB.description:
Mikel Merino’s first-half header was enough to win a hotly-contested London derby against Chelsea.

The Spaniard – starting his sixth consecutive game up front – flicked in Martin Odegaard’s corner to give us a deserved lead on 20 minutes.

There were few clear-cut chances for either side after that, though Merino came closest to doubling our advantage in the second-half, with a well-struck volley that Robert Sanchez batted away.

But the one goal was enough to consolidate our second-position in the table, while also making it seven successive Premier League games against Chelsea without defeat.

We racked up six attempts in an opening 20 minutes full of attacking intent.

Within the first five minutes Jurrien Timber headed a corner wide of the near post before Leandro Trossard skewed a shot wide when he had a bit of time to set his shot on the edge of the box.

Gabriel Martinelli – back in the starting lineup for the first time for over a month – was presented with our next chance from a wayward Sanchez pass. His shot was straight at the Spaniard though.

Chelsea survived a penalty shout for handball against Marc Cucurella, who appeared to divert the ball away from Timber with his arm as he fell. We carried on, and after a scramble in the six-yard box, Declan Rice blasted his shot over.

Rice then struck wide from 25 yards as we continued to put the visitors under pressure. Trossard was next to try his luck. Sanchez failed to collect a cross, but our Belgian forward scuffed his right-footed attempt off target.

The goal was coming, and eventually our pressure paid off. Martinelli ran at Benoit Badiashile on the right to win a corner, which Odegaard swung in from the left. Merino ran across the front post, and flicked his header over Sanchez.

Chelsea were fortunate to still have 11 men on the pitch when Wesley Fofana survived a VAR review after an apparent stamp on Rice.

It had been one-way traffic from the opening half hour, but Chelsea nearly drew level when Cucurella’s speculative shot squirmed through David Raya’s grasp but luckily just the wrong side of the upright.

It was a warning from the visitors who were slowly starting to build up possession. We finished the first-half back on top though, and Trossard so nearly set up Odegaard inside the area, but his pass was intercepted.

It was a slower start to the second half, but we woke up when Martinelli’s deep cross fell beautifully onto the left boot of Merino. He cracked his volley goalwards but Sanchez parried the effort on his goalline.

Odegaard was the next to draw a save from Sanchez, but his first-time left footed effort inside the area lacked power.

Rice saw his free-kick deflected wide after Myles Lewis-Skelly earned the set piece with a positive driving run.

There was less goalmouth action in the second-half, but the intensity remained, and both sides had three players in the book by the 70th minute.

Mikel Arteta sent on Ethan Nwaneri late on, but we couldn’t add to the scoreline, making for a fairly edgy last 15 minutes, though in truth Raya remained untroubled in goal.

pa.title: ਕੀ ਤੁਸੀਂ ਇੱਕ ਸਵੈ-ਚਲਾਉਣ ਵਾਲੀ ਕਾਰ ਨੂੰ ਠੱਗ ਸਕਦੇ ਹੋ?
pa.description:
ਲੇਜ਼ਰਾਂ ਦੀ ਤਾਕਤ ਨੂੰ ਕਦੇ ਘਟਾ ਨਾ ਅੰਕਣਾ! ਇਕ ਇੰਜੀਨੀਅਰ ਵਾਂਗ ਸੋਚਣਾ ਸਿੱਖਣ ਵਿੱਚ ਮਜ਼ਾ ਆਉ ਜਾਂਦਾ ਹੈ ਅਤੇ http://crunchlabs.com/Lidar 'ਤੇ 2 ਮੁਫਤ ਬਾਕਸ ਪ੍ਰਾਪਤ ਕਰੋ।

ਆਪਣਾ ਕ੍ਰੰਚ ਲੈਬਸ ਬਾਕਸ ਅੱਜ ਹੀ ਪ੍ਰਾਪਤ ਕਰੋ:
ਬੱਚਿਆਂ ਲਈ ਬਿਲਡ ਬਾਕਸ ਇੱਥੇ ਕਲਿੱਕ ਕਰੋ: http://crunchlabs.com/Lidar
ਟੀਨ ਏਜਰ ਅਤੇ ਵੱਡਿਆਂ ਲਈ ਹੈਕ ਪੈਕ ਇੱਥੇ ਕਲਿੱਕ ਕਰੋ: http://crunchlabs.com/LidarHP

ਸਾਡੇ ਨਾਲ ਆਪਣੀ ਲਾਈਡਰ ਕਾਰ ਟੈਸਟ ਕਰਨ ਲਈ ਲੂਮਿਨਾਰ ਦਾ ਧੰਨਵਾਦ: https://www.luminartech.com/

ਰਾਕ ਰੋਬੋਟਿਕ ਦੇ ਹੈਰਿਸਨ @IndianaDrones ਦਾ ਧੰਨਵਾਦ ਜੋ ਆਪਣੇ ਬਹੁਤ ਕੂਲ ਲਾਈਡਰ ਨਾਲ ਮਦਦ ਕਰਨ ਲਈ ਸਾਨੂੰ ਮਿਲੇ। ਇਸ ਪ੍ਰਜੈਕਟ ਤੋਂ ਸਕੈਨਸ ਅਤੇ ਕ੍ਰੰਚ ਲੈਬਸ ਦਾ 3D ਟੂਰ ਦੇਖਣ ਲਈ ਤੁਸੀਂ https://www.rockrobotic.com/ 'ਤੇ ਜਾ ਸਕਦੇ ਹੋ।

ਵੀਡੀਓ ਵਿੱਚ ਕੁਝ ਸੰਗੀਤ ਪ੍ਰਦਾਨ ਕਰਨ ਲਈ ਇਨ੍ਹਾਂ ਲੋਕਾਂ ਦਾ ਧੰਨਵਾਦ:
ਪੌਂਡਰ - @Pondermusic   
ਲੌਰਾ ਸ਼ਿਗਿਹਾਰਾ - @supershigi   
ਐਂਡਰੂ ਐਪਲਪੀ - https://soundcloud.com/andrewapplepie
ਬਲਿਊ ਵੇਡਨਸਡੇ - https://soundcloud.com/bluewednesday
ਦਾਨੀਜਲ ਜ਼ੈਂਬੋ - https://open.spotify.com/intl-de/artist/1ZD9ri2wmZZPL4qs92sXZX?si=iI7jkn-qSY-6NKo931314Q

te.title: మీరు స్వయంచాలిత కార్‌ని మోసం చేయగలరా?
te.description:
ఫ్రీకిన్' లేసర్స్ శక్తిని అస్సలు తక్కువ అంచనా వేయకండి! ఇంజనీర్లలా ఆలోచించడం నేర్చుకోవడంలో సరదాగా గడపండి మరియు 2 ఉచిత బాక్స్‌లను పొందండి: http://crunchlabs.com/Lidar

మీ క్రంచ్‌లాబ్స్ బాక్స్‌ను ఈ రోజు పొందండి:
పిల్లల కోసం బిల్డ్ బాక్స్ ఇవ్వరానికి ఇక్కడ క్లిక్ చేయండి: http://crunchlabs.com/Lidar

snippet.title: Nørgaard scores and Wissa nets again 🤩 | AFC Bournemouth 1-2 Brentford | Premier League Highlights
snippet.description:
Yoane Wissa and Christian Nørgaard were on target as Brentford came from behind to beat Bournemouth 2-1 in an entertaining encounter at Vitality Stadium.

A Vitaly Janelt own goal gave the Cherries an early lead, but Wissa’s header saw the sides go in for the break on level terms. Nørgaard struck midway through the second half to earn the Bees a fifth straight away win in the Premier League.

snippet.title: MASIH SALING PEDULI, NATASHA - DESTA BAKAL RUJUK ?? (NATASHA RIZKY)
snippet.description:
Yuhuu ada Natasha Rizky datang kesini, kalian pasti sudah tidak asing lagi sama public figure yang satu ini??
Natasha Rizky Pradita lahir pada tanggal 23 November 1993.
Ia memulai langkahnya di dunia hiburan dengan mengikuti pemilihan Gadis Sampul pada tahun 2008, Natasha Rizky tidak hanya sukses di dunia hiburan, tetapi juga aktif dalam Menulis buku. 

Di podcast kali ini, Natasha Rizky akan berbagi kisah di balik cerita dari buku-buku yang dia tulis.

Bagaimana keseruannya? Saksikan hanya di Curhat bang kali ini bersama Natasha Rizky.

snippet.description:
Kupas Abis! Ini Alasan Raffi Ahmad Membantu Mami Nunung | SURPRISE MAK!!

Surprise Mak!! Pagi Hari Makin Seru dan Penuh Kejutan di RCTI
Talkshow seru – Obrolan menarik bersama bintang tamu spesial yang berbagi cerita dan pengalaman seru.
Penampilan musisi keren – Sajian musik penuh kejutan yang siap menghibur pagi kamu.
Games seru – Penonton di studio dan di rumah berkesempatan memenangkan hadiah uang tunai.
Kejutan tak terduga – Berbagai kejutan menarik yang bikin kamu semakin penasaran!
Acara ini menghadirkan panggung penuh kejutan dengan berbagai permainan seru, mulai dari tebak lagu, joget bareng, hingga tantangan memasak. Tidak hanya menghibur penonton di studio, tetapi juga pemirsa di rumah yang bisa mendapatkan hadiah uang tunai serta kejutan spesial lainnya.

Saksikan Surprise Mak!! mulai 24 Februari, setiap Senin – Jumat pukul 08.15 WIB, live hanya di RCTI melalui kanal digital 28 UHF untuk pemirsa Jabodetabek.

Exciting talk show – Interesting chats with special guest stars who share exciting stories and experiences.

snippet.title: Nyerenteng di Babak Kadua ⚽⚽⚽⚽ | Match Highlight Semen Padang FC 1-4 PERSIB
snippet.description:
PERSIB menjauh dari kejaran para pesaingnya dalam perburuan gelar juara Liga 1 2024/25 setelah mengalahkan Semen Padang 4-1 atas Semen Padang pada pertandingan pekan ke-27 di Stadion Haji Agus Salim Padang, Senin, 10 Maret 2025.

snippet.description:

Rina mendapat telepon dari Budenya untuk membantu membersihkan rumah nenek di desa utuk dijual, mendengar bahwa dia akan mendapat bonus, Rina pun setuju dan mulai membersihkan rumah neneknya yang besar dan tradisional. snippet.title: Italian Bake Rice Buatan Bude Wiji Istimewa Banget | Galeri 4 (2/8) | MASTERCHEF INDONESIA
snippet.description:
Bude Wiji berhasil mencuri perhatian para juri dengan hidangan Italian Baked Rice yang luar biasa! Chef Rudy memuji keistimewaan cita rasa masakan Bude Wiji, sementara Chef Renatta terlihat sangat menikmati setiap suapan. Perpaduan rasa gurih, tekstur yang sempurna, dan sentuhan khas Bude Wiji membuat hidangan ini menjadi sorotan. Apakah ini akan menjadi hidangan terbaik di tantangan kali ini?

=========

Selamat datang di Channel MasterChef Indonesia Season 12. 🎉

Chef Juna, Chef Rudy Choirudin & Chef Renatta Moeloek akan mencari 
siapa yang pantas menjadi the next MasterChef Indonesia Season 12!

Kompetisi memasak terbesar yang pastinya sayang untuk kamu lewatkan!
Jadi siapa kontestan favoritmu pada season ini?

SAKSIKAN! MasterChef Indonesia Season 12 Mulai Sabtu & Minggu 
Pukul 15.45 WIB hanya di RCTI!


#MasterChefIndonesiaSeason12 #MCIS12 #chefRenatta

그 어떤 미래도
저 멀리 있는 미래에도
내 곁에 머물러 있어 줘

snippet.title: NAPAK TILAS TAHUN 1960, RATUSAN RIBU TIONGHOA INDONESIA DIPULANGKAN KE TIONGKOK
snippet.description:
Join this channel to get access to perks:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCPs6VifaJFfIxRFf1wYhq9w/join

Kebun Tionghoa Perantauan Changshan berlokasi di Kabupaten Yunxiao, Zhangzhou, Provinsi Fujian Tiongkok. Changshan  dikenal sebagai kebun Tionghoa Perantauan terbesar kedua di Tiongkok, yang menampung "Guiqiao" dari 18 negara yang pulan ke Tiongkok mulai tahun 1950an hingga akhir tahun 1970an.. "Guiqiao" adalah sebutan bagi Tionghoa Perantauan yang kembali ke Tiongkok pada tahun 1960-an. 

Sekembalinya ke China, mereka tidak pernah melupakan Indonesia, tetap mempertahankan tradisi Indonesia dalam kehidupan sehari-hari, bahkan mewariskan seni budaya dan kuliner Indonesia ke anak cucu mereka. 
Ikuti terus video saya untuk menguak lebih banyak kisah dan cerita dari para Guiqiao Indonesia di tempat ini.

Jangan lupa terus dukung channel aku dengan LIKE, COMMENT dan SHARE video ini. Dukungan kalian sangat berarti bagi saya dalam mengembangkan channel ini. Terima kasih teman-teman 🙏

snippet.title: Satu Hukuman yang Mengubah Politik Dunia Selamanya
snippet.description:

snippet.title: INDONESIA MINI DI CHINA ❓BANYAK MAKANAN INDONESIA, Semuanya Fasih BAHASA INDONESIA
snippet.description:
Kebun Tionghoa Perantauan Changshan berlokasi di Kabupaten Yunxiao, Zhangzhou, Provinsi Fujian Tiongkok. Changshan  dikenal sebagai kebun Tionghoa Perantauan terbesar kedua di Tiongkok, yang menampung "Guiqiao" dari 18 negara yang pulan ke Tiongkok mulai tahun 1950an hingga akhir tahun 1970an.. "Guiqiao" adalah sebutan bagi Tionghoa Perantauan yang kembali ke Tiongkok pada tahun 1960-an. 

Sekembalinya ke China, mereka tidak pernah melupakan Indonesia, tetap mempertahankan tradisi Indonesia dalam kehidupan sehari-hari, bahkan mewariskan seni budaya dan kuliner Indonesia ke anak cucu mereka. 
Ikuti terus video saya untuk menguak lebih banyak kisah dan cerita dari para Guiqiao Indonesia di tempat ini.

Jangan lupa terus dukung channel aku dengan LIKE, COMMENT dan SHARE video ini. Dukungan kalian sangat berarti bagi saya dalam mengembangkan channel ini. Terima kasih teman-teman 🙏

snippet.title: LEGENDA SITU BAGENDIT: Keserakahan Nyai Endit Berujung Petaka | Cerita Rakyat | Kisah Nusantara
snippet.description:
Ketamakan bisa membawa bencana! Ini adalah kisah legendaris dari tanah Pasundan tentang seorang janda kaya bernama Nyai Endit, yang serakah dan kejam terhadap rakyatnya.
Di sebuah desa subur di utara Garut, Nyai Endit memanfaatkan kesulitannya untuk menindas para petani, membeli hasil panen dengan harga murah, dan menjualnya kembali dengan harga tinggi. Kesombongannya semakin menjadi-jadi, hingga suatu hari seorang pengemis tua misterius datang meminta makan. Alih-alih menolong, Nyai Endit malah mengusirnya dengan kasar.
Namun, siapa sangka, pengemis itu ternyata memiliki kekuatan gaib! snippet.title: BETRAND PUTRA ONSU - DIAM DIAM (OFFICIAL MUSIC VIDEO)
snippet.description:
Diam-Diam Betrand Putra Onsu kembali merilis karya terbarunya! Setelah sukses dengan single "Bila Memang Kamu" yang viral, Betrand Putra Onsu kembali menghadirkan karya terbarunya di tahun 2025. Kali ini, penyanyi dengan suara khas ini merilis single berjudul "Diam-Diam," sebuah lagu yang menggambarkan penyesalan seseorang yang baru menyadari kehilangan cinta tulus dalam hidupnya.
 
Ditulis oleh penulis yang telah menghasilkan lagu-lagu hits yaitu Tintin dan Clara Riva, single "Diam-Diam" menceritakan tentang seseorang yang diam-diam masih mencintai sosok yang pernah hadir dalam hidupnya. Ia menyesal telah menyia-nyiakan cinta sejati dan kini berharap bisa kembali memperbaiki semuanya. Lirik yang dipadukan dengan warna vokal Betrand sangat khas membuat lagu ini sangat releatble untuk pendengar yang pernah mengalami kehilangan dalam hubungan.

Dengan aransemen yang dibawakan sekaligus dipadukan dengan genre pop modern membuat single terbaru dari Betrand Putra Onsu ini seakan bisa membawa para pendengar hanyut didalam musik dan liriknya.
 
Diam-Diam sudah tersedia di seluruh digital platform music kesayangan kamu! Betrand juga merilis music video dari single ini yang diperankan langsung oleh Betrand. Music Video dari “Diam-Diam” sudah bisa disaksikan di channel Youtube HITS Records. Enjoy!

Listen on all music platform: https://bfan.link/diam-diam
